title: The Result Of Doing My Best To Not To Get Killed By My Brother In Another World! - Novel Updates
genre: Comedy   Romance   School Life   Shoujo   Slice of Life
tags: Cute Protagonist   Cute Story   Dense Protagonist   Fantasy World   Indecisive Protagonist   Knights   Lack of Common Sense   Overprotective Siblings   Reincarnated in Another World   Reincarnation   Saints   Shoujo-Ai Subplot   Siblings
author: Kuramoto Shima   倉本縞
description:
In a novel I read in a previous life, I was killed for the crime of deceiving a saint.

And the person who killed me was my brother. He is a scary and strong brother called the Count of Darkness.

Every day I’m terrified of what will happen if my brother ends up killing me, but something is wrong with him.

He’s supposed to kill me, but he’s saying he’s going to protect me. What in the world is going on ……?>
